🫣 What if you could look inside Figma files of top designers for free?

I was tired of binge-watching design tutorials on YouTube because they lacked real world constraints.

So, I'm launching a new interview series, 'Sneak Peek,' which shows how top designers use @figma.

Here's the stellar lineup of companies and designers featured in season 1:

